metadata.description:
FUTURE ABSTRACT (AI) is the new AI series by Duo.
This collection is a project that combining the latest technology.

Owners of CYBER SKULL (SERIES)  and  FUTURE ABSTRACT (AI)  will get new combinations created based on the purchased abstract NFT. 

This is a story of art in which artists and collectors can participate.
